** Company and Role: **   
  
We are searching for an experienced Engineering Manager to join one of
Australia’s largest digital innovators. You will have the opportunity to work
with an agile team of high performers to deliver complex features and
improvements in an established, but progressive environment. If you are a
confident leader looking to make an impact on business-critical systems, we’d
love to talk to you! Here’s what we’re looking for:  
  
** The ideal fit: **   
  
A "lead from the front" management style working with cloud native
technologies including of PHP, Go (or similar), Micro-service architecture and
Docker.  

  * Inspiring and mentoring teams in building Scalable and Robust quality solutions 
  * Managing Agile environments – TDD – CI/CD 
  * Ability to mentor teams in best practice 
  * Experience with operating production-level service in an enterprise environment 
  * Prior experience working with e-commerce products or platforms advantageous – UX - UI 
  
